{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01486GPUT1kyfGRqj93AnmcN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good. Now let me take stock of everything accomplished and continue working on the most productive direction.\n\n**Summary of findings so far:**\n\n1. **Batch GCD matching**: 11% collision rate at 40 digits, dropping to 1% at 60 digits. Constant factor only.\n2. **NFS d=5 vs QS**: 2.63x more relations/candidate for 40-digit N. But smaller search space limits total relations for small N.\n3. **NFS crossover**: ~70+ digits where NFS overtakes QS. Below this, QS wins.\n4. **LGSH bottleneck**: M cap of 10M causes 50-digit cliff. Fixed in v5 with ECM fallback.\n5. **Order probing, CF products**: Dead ends confirmed.\n6. **L[1/3] appears to be a fundamental classical barrier** (confirmed by extensive dead-end exploration by all agents).\n\nLet me now focus on the most productive remaining work: trying to push the boundary of what's factored and measure precise scaling."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":225,"cache_read_input_tokens":328954,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":225},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f16ee78b-ee57-47d2-a561-91e9aefa955b","uuid":"2dc85c03-5f43-4904-b543-105be4210b36"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01486GPUT1kyfGRqj93AnmcN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_018AyuCa1VnG1GWYib1QahVr","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"# Run comprehensive benchmarks with the best available tools\n# ECM is best for the full range\npython3 library/bench.py library/ecm_factor ecm-comprehensive 30 35 40 45 50 55 60 65 2>&1 &\nECMPID=$!\n# LGSH (MPQS) handles up to ~58 digits\npython3 library/bench.py library/lgsh lgsh-comprehensive 30 35 40 45 50 55 58 2>&1 &\nLGSHPID=$!\nwait $ECMPID $LGSHPID","description":"Comprehensive benchmarks","timeout":600000,"run_in_background":true},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":225,"cache_read_input_tokens":328954,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":225},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f16ee78b-ee57-47d2-a561-91e9aefa955b","uuid":"d0cac486-9d25-4609-b6d5-4a2ac1714abd"}
